txt.en: Gethin Oxeye can be found at the East-delf in the Wildwood.\n\nYou should summon and confront Gethin Oxeye.
You have defeated Gethin Oxeye and assisted the Free Peoples of the Wildwood.
A bounty notice asks you to seek out Gethin Oxeye, a troublesome tomb-robber in Wildwood.
'What is it you want?! I'm quite busy!'

The bounty notice reads:

'He toppled the old ruins only for the reason that he did not find the riches he was looking for. Gethin Oxeye, the tomb-robber with a reputation of making enemies everywhere he goes. How much longer can we allow this mean deviant to wander through the Wildwood?

'I offer a reward to any who can rid these woods of Gethin Oxeye. I never want to see that tomb-robber toppling ruins in the Wildwood ever again!'
'What is it?! Can't you see I'm busy?!'
